Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting pretty chilly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not too friendly today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just get off work, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All the restaurants in this area are already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the hotel, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who live on this street...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,for some reason, they all know me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,called me "Anna."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:10.75,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,800)\pos(360,340)}The Door to Nightmares
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Suk, a suspected serial\Nkiller, is hospitalized here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there aren't any police officers or patrol cars around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, there's no point unless I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no sign of police anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A patient named Suk should be registered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a number of casualties from\Nan abandoned building on Brno Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the one where a bunch of unemployed\Nmen got into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployed men?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't understand what they said on the news, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that must be their cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which rooms are they in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They were seriously wounded, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they were all transferred out after receiving treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,An ambulance came and took all six of them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Six men attacked us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Detective Jan Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any patients who were\Nadmitted with gunshot wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no record of an emergency patient\Nnamed Jan Suk being brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Research documents and a tape\Npertaining to 511 kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Petrov, who was the former director of 511 kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and operated an unauthorized orphanage in Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,entrusted me with them right before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And who exactly is after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I don't actually know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But the former Czechoslovakian secret\Npolice definitely want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the documents and the tape right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have them on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being held at a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of them, Detective Suk was seriously injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and abducted from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what they'll do to Suk in order\Nto get their hands on what they want...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do those things say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The documents are full of research data with\Ntechnical terms along with a roster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take a good look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I only listened to the tape briefly, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was recorded on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice of a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably interrogated after being drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked for his name, he answered "Johan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,511 kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Research documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the tape right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's conduct business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to become\Nfurther involved in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have something I'd like to ask the\Nformer Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem now is whether or not\Nthese people will actually talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you're inviting us to dinner, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's a bigshot in the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I looked them up at the newspaper agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Colonel Karel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the top man decided to come himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies for my subordinates\Ntreating you so roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to a miscommunication in our command structure,\Nwe have an unexpected situation on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We are currently suffering from\Na serious misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By you, and by society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we're a group of killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been placed in a hospital where we have connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He has not been harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We did not kill anyone in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that blonde girl acting on your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have reports about her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,she has absolutely no ties with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We are extremely inconvenienced by her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What we want aren't human lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine in Germany wanted\Nthose documents and the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we had cautiously approached\NPetrov many times to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he was targeted and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there must've been lots of money involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to have the documents\Nand the tape in exchange for Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's avoid such talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that must not be repeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If something like that existed in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows what could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that must never be repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us put aside that sort of talk for now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with this business negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm from that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm from 511 kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you leave there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, when I was fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When were you put in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably when I was seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 1963, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the early 60s...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was officially stationed in Berlin as an intelligence\Nofficer for the Czechoslovakian embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She married a German.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But she and her husband tried to defect by crossing\Nthe Berlin Wall and they were shot to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And only that boy was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,On paper, that place provided a wonderful environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,An ideal, educational environment\Nwhere children with a past...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,would be nurtured into the elites who would\Nshoulder the communism of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed the papers that allowed that child\Nto be placed in 511 kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that happened there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or from before I went there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know my real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to change something so horrible into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even trying to sell documents containing\Nexperimental data on your own nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears we've gone off topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to think of this\Nas a beneficial business deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are free to go for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope for a positive answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them back with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the most important thing is to rescue Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you agree to his demands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he will release Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The cocoa he had once a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked forward to the weekly cocoa ration!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I had a fever and was lying in the infirmary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,he brought me some cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His own cocoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he loved it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had such delicious cocoa before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to do something to repay him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, it was popular among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about ourselves to our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't really understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but our memories were fading...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with the strange classes we attended every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We were even in danger of forgetting our own names...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we had our friends remember who we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved to draw pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And he loved insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't like to collect insects because\Nhe had to kill them, and he didn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The most fun he had was when he went\Ninto the forest with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He caught lots of butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But he released all the butterflies from\Nthe bug cage on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,His dream was to become an entomologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Reinhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't hide things from him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}can become anything.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, welcome back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, welcome back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, welcome back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The road leading to this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This storefront signboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this door, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know them, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought things over last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like you to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither those documents nor the tape\Nhave anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like we have time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they can't wait for more negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Czechoslovakian secret police have\Nbothered to come all the way but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to think things over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of giving you either\Nthe tape or the research documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care what happens to Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything were to happen to Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the tape and research documents would be lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not start this kind of meaningless negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let you listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,On one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forget your business deal with\Nyour German friend who's trying to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to listen to it because of a personal interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm willing to let you listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}should{\i} listen to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of the nephew you\Nplaced in 511 kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You should listen to the voice of the boy named\NJohan who was recorded on the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not making any deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,someone might be killed because of that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people involved with your\NCzechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think have been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the person who wants that tape the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of the voice that was recorded on that tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've learned what that tape\Nis from your German friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he tell you to get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"The true identity of the monster..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get you people involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,before more people are killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So Johan was tracing his own roots...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and came to Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be trying to erase everything, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what did you people do fifteen years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a family living near Cedok\NBridge in the Michalska district.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, they were taken away by the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After taking him away from the building\Nwith the three frogs on its signboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what did you guys do to Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big brother...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As if being dragged down these stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he was taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that at the time, I was in a position\Nto receive all the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But these three frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And a family being taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absolutely no recollection of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there was information that didn't reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the things that man did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know which division of the\Nsecret police he belonged to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,nor did I know whose command he was under.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he could detain anyone\Nfreely without reporting to his superiors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he was doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was just a lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he was given a luxurious mansion as his workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was known as the "Man of the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that man was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a quiet man with an extremely elegant demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't wear a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and liked tea and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What was his name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz... Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't know if that was his real name or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,since he also had a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also the author of a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of this door, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was reading a picture book in here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone opened the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and came home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very peculiar picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The title was "The Monster Without\NA Name," or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this... memory...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been reading a picture book in here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who opened the door and came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm welcoming myself back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Gazing at what is known now in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:23:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Your eyes believe in kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:53.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Scariest Thing
